26:17.458 --> 26:20.041
SHE'S GOT IT.

26:20.083 --> 26:22.000
SHE'S GOOD.

26:22.041 --> 26:24.834
OKAY, LET'S PREPARE TO CLOSE.

26:27.625 --> 26:30.041
