THEY'RE TRYING TO HAVE KIDS?

26:35.000 --> 26:37.625
ABSOLUTELY. JUDAISM IS UNIQUE
AMONG THE MAJOR WORLD RELIGIONS

26:37.667 --> 26:40.125
IN THAT IT PROMOTES SEX
NOT JUST FOR PROCREATION

26:40.166 --> 26:41.959
BUT FOR PLEASURE.

26:42.000 --> 26:44.834
YOU SEE? YOU SHOULD COME
TO SHUL MORE OFTEN.

26:44.875 --> 26:47.041
