ALL SORTS OF GOOD THINGS.

26:47.083 --> 26:49.208
THAT'S GOOD. SEX IS GOOD.

26:49.250 --> 26:52.083
BUT EVEN IF PEOPLE ARE JUST
HAVING SEX FOR PLEASURE,

26:52.125 --> 26:55.333
BABIES HAPPEN.
AND YOU WANT TO KNOW
ABOUT BIRTH CONTROL.

26:55.375 --> 26:57.959
YOU SHOULD READ
THE STORY OF ONAN.

26:58.000 --> 27:00.041
WE'RE PRETTY DOWN ON ANYTHING
THAT HAS TO DO WITH

27:00.083 --> 27:02.709
DESTRUCTION OF THE SEED.
WELL, THE PILL DOESN'T
TECHNICALLY DESTROY ANY SEED.

27:02.750 --> 27:05.875
YOU'RE RIGHT. IT--IT'S ALL
ABOUT INTERPRETATION.

27:05.917 --> 27:08.166
DEPENDING UPON HOW OBSERVANT
THEY ARE, SOME JEWS FEEL

27:08.208 --> 27:11.166
THAT IF YOU'VE HAD
AT LEAST ONE BOY AND ONE GIRL,

27:11.208 --> 27:12.792
YOU'VE BEEN FRUITFUL ENOUGH.

27:12.834 --> 27:14.458
