THOSE--THOSE MITZVAHS?

27:24.500 --> 27:26.458
LOOK, RABBIS HAVE BEEN
DEBATING THESE RULES

27:26.500 --> 27:29.375
FOR HUNDRED OF YEARS.
SO CAN'T WE FIND ONE WHO WOULD
LET 'EM USE BIRTH CONTROL?

27:29.417 --> 27:32.000
