HE WAS GONNA DO SOMETHING AWFUL,

29:45.083 --> 29:47.041
LIKE MAKE SOME BIG SPEECH

29:47.083 --> 29:49.041
ABOUT UPHOLDING
THE MONTGOMERY NAME

29:49.083 --> 29:50.959
OR SOME SNARKY POSTMORTEM,

29:51.000 --> 29:53.000
