29:53.041 --> 29:56.375
HE CALLED IT ELEGANT.

29:56.417 --> 29:59.500
IT WAS NICE.

29:59.542 --> 30:01.917
WHAT?
OH, BOY.

30:01.959 --> 30:04.792
WHAT?
DON'T HATE ME, ADDIE.

30:04.834 --> 30:07.291
I AM YOUR FRIEND.

30:07.333 --> 30:10.333
