AND I KNOW WHAT THAT DID TO YOU,

30:13.792 --> 30:16.083
AND I WANT TO BE YOUR FRIEND
AND I DON'T WANT

30:16.125 --> 30:19.709
TO KEEP SECRETS FROM YOU--
OH, MY GOD, NAI.
YOU SLEPT WITH THE CAPTAIN.

30:19.750 --> 30:23.041
NO, NO, ADDIE. NO, I WOULDN'T.
OH, OKAY. THANK GOD.
(exhales deeply)

30:23.083 --> 30:25.166
OKAY, FOR A MINUTE,
YOU SCARED ME THERE.

30:25.208 --> 30:27.792
I THOUGHT--
VIOLET SLEPT WITH HIM.

30:27.834 --> 30:29.625
AND--AND VIOLET TOLD CHARLOTTE,

30:29.667 --> 30:31.208
AND CHARLOTTE TOLD COOPER,

30:31.250 --> 30:33.750
AND THEN SAM READ IT
ALL OVER COOPER'S FACE,

30:33.792 --> 30:36.834
