IF YOU WANTED TO KNOW,

30:36.875 --> 30:40.166
SO HE ASKED ME, AND I...
I'M SORRY, ADDIE.

30:41.792 --> 30:44.041
I COULDN'T NOT TELL YOU.

30:44.083 --> 30:46.000
(sighs)

30:50.458 --> 30:53.208
YOU NEED TO JUST LET IT GO,
ADDIE. OKAY? IT'S NOT ABOUT YOU.

30:53.250 --> 30:54.834
