YOU'RE THE FIRST ONE
I CAN ACTUALLY ASK.

38:19.041 --> 38:22.000
OKAY, UM, IF YOU--
IF YOU REALLY WANT TO KNOW,

38:22.041 --> 38:25.458
IT WAS, UM...
IT WAS WONDERFUL.

38:25.500 --> 38:27.458
(scoffs)
NO, I'M--I'M SORRY
IF--IF THAT HURTS YOU

38:27.500 --> 38:29.667
OR IF IT DOESN'T JIBE
WITH HOW YOU SEE HIM,

38:29.709 --> 38:31.333
BUT HE WAS KIND AND CARING.

38:31.375 --> 38:34.041
HE WAS A REAL GENTLEMAN.
HE HELPED ME.

38:34.083 --> 38:36.542
HE'S THE FIRST PERSON
IN A LONG TIME

38:36.583 --> 38:38.500
THAT MADE ME FEEL NORMAL.

38:38.542 --> 38:42.041
AND MAYBE I WAS WRONG FOR
DOING IT, MAYBE WE BOTH WERE,

38:42.083 --> 38:44.041
BUT HE'S NOT A BAD PERSON.

38:44.083 --> 38:47.000
AND I DIDN'T MEAN
TO HURT YOU, ADDISON--
WELL, BUT YOU DID IT ANYWAY.

38:47.041 --> 38:49.417
WELL, YOU TOLD PETE.
DID YOU MEAN TO HURT HIM?

38:49.458 --> 38:51.041
THAT'S DIFFERENT.

38:51.083 --> 38:53.625
BUT YOU DID IT ANYWAY.

38:53.667 --> 38:57.083
(Kate Earl's "Can't Treat Me
That Way" playing)

38:57.125 --> 38:59.500
GET OUT.
BUT, DADDY, I DON'T THINK--

38:59.542 --> 39:02.166
GET OUT OF THIS CAR,
GO IN THE HOUSE

39:02.208 --> 39:06.000
APOLOGIZE TO YOUR MOTHER
AND MEAN IT,

39:06.041 --> 39:09.041
BECAUSE IF YOU
SCREW UP AGAIN...

39:09.083 --> 39:11.041
♪♪♪

39:11.083 --> 39:13.166
SHE WILL KILL YOU.

39:13.208 --> 39:16.083
AND I WILL HELP HER
HIDE THE BODY THIS TIME.

39:16.125 --> 39:18.583
SO... GO.

39:18.625 --> 39:20.792
♪ WE BLEW INTO SPACE ♪

39:20.834 --> 39:22.208
♪ INTO SPACE ♪

39:22.250 --> 39:25.041
♪ A COMMON LOVER'S RIFT ♪

39:25.083 --> 39:28.041
♪ UNCOMMON WORDS
THROWN LIKE FISTS ♪

39:28.083 --> 39:30.250
♪ 'CAUSE IF YOU MEANT IT, BABY ♪

39:30.291 --> 39:33.041
♪ IT'S TOO LATE ♪

39:33.083 --> 39:35.667
♪ YOU'VE GOT A WOMAN
THAT KNOWS HER WORTH ♪

39:35.709 --> 39:38.583
♪ AND AIN'T PREPARED
TO COMPROMISE IT ♪

39:38.625 --> 39:40.542
♪ YOU BETTER LISTEN,
YOU BETTER... ♪

39:40.583 --> 39:43.542
I LOVE HER, BUT, MAN, SH--

39:43.583 --> 39:45.792
I KNOW.

39:45.834 --> 39:48.041
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO, SAM?

39:48.083 --> 39:52.458
WHAT IF SHE KEEPS THIS UP?
WHAT'S THE NEXT STEP?
WE GOTTA STAY TOUGH...

39:52.500 --> 39:55.041
STAY TOGETHER ON THIS.

39:55.083 --> 39:59.417
♪ YOU CAN'T TREAT ME THAT WAY ♪

39:59.458 --> 40:03.875
♪ OOH ♪

40:03.917 --> 40:05.417
♪ OOH ♪

40:05.458 --> 40:08.667
ADDISON?

40:08.709 --> 40:11.875
I HAVE TOLERATED THEM.

40:11.917 --> 40:13.875
I MAY NOT HAVE FORGIVEN YOU,

40:13.917 --> 40:16.041
BUT I HAVE TOLERATED THEM ALL.

40:16.083 --> 40:17.667
THIS IS DIFFERENT.

40:17.709 --> 40:20.083
SHE'S A CONSENTING ADULT.
NO, SHE IS NOT.

40:20.125 --> 40:22.667
IN ADDITION TO BEING MY FRIEND
AND MY COLLEAGUE,

40:22.709 --> 40:25.458
VIOLET IS DAMAGED.
I UNDERSTAND
THAT'S HOW YOU SEE HER--

40:25.500 --> 40:28.500
YOU TOOK ADVANTAGE.
I DON'T THINK VIOLET FEELS
TAKEN ADVANTAGE OF.

40:28.542 --> 40:31.041
SHE DOESN'T.
SHE CALLED YOU A GENTLEMAN.

40:31.083 --> 40:33.041
SHE SAID THAT YOU
WERE WONDERFUL TO HER.

40:33.083 --> 40:35.625
YOU KNOW, AND AS BAD
AS I'VE FELT ABOUT MYSELF

40:35.667 --> 40:37.625
FOR COVERING FOR YOU
FOR ALL OF THESE YEARS,

40:37.667 --> 40:39.709
AND AS DEPRESSING AS IT IS

40:39.750 --> 40:41.709
TO WATCH ARCHER
FOLLOW IN YOUR FOOTSTEPS...

40:41.750 --> 40:43.709
(voice breaking) NOTHING
COMPARED TO HEARING THAT,

40:43.750 --> 40:45.709
BECAUSE IT MADE ME WONDER,
DADDY.

40:45.750 --> 40:48.083
WHY IS IT
THAT YOU CAN BE SO GOOD

40:48.125 --> 40:50.083
TO EVERY WOMAN IN THE WORLD

40:50.125 --> 40:53.709
EXCEPT BIZZY AND ME?

40:53.750 --> 40:57.208
ESPECIALLY WHEN WE'RE THE ONES
THAT LOVE YOU THE MOST.

40:57.250 --> 40:58.834
♪ ...TO COMPROMISE IT ♪

40:58.875 --> 41:01.792
♪ YOU BETTER LISTEN,
YOU BETTER MAKE IT BETTER ♪

41:01.834 --> 41:04.166
♪ BUT DON'T MAKE ME SAY ♪

41:04.208 --> 41:08.291
♪ YOU CAN'T TREAT ME THAT WAY ♪

41:08.333 --> 41:09.917
♪ OH ♪

41:09.959 --> 41:11.125
♪ OH ♪

41:11.166 --> 41:13.583
BIZZY, HI.

41:13.625 --> 41:16.583
LISTEN, IF YOU DON'T COME OUT
HERE AND TELL HER THE TRUTH,

41:16.625 --> 41:17.875
I WILL.
